title: From "Murder House" to "Apocalypse": Billie Dean Howard predicted almost everything
author: American Horror Story 10
comment: OMG PLEASE DO MORE VIDEOS LIKE THIS ONE! Best ahs page! well done!
Also small detail you missed. In one of the episodes she mentions how certain places have bad energies to them. One of the places she gave as an example was asylums.
This makes me wonder if Ryan knew what EVERY season would be from the very start
Also she told Violet several times how she was gifted and talented and how ashamed she was that she wasted it (by dying) but she inadvertently predicted coven through this, as Zoe is very talented.
description: She has a key-role in AHS.
